column10:
Much better than The Division 2, Love this game. Great for single players and also people who love that PVP action. play how you want. Be good, be bad.. it's up to you. You feel like you in the world and trying to help people. There are NPC's wondering around (they not in Division 2) and you get to help them. they give great Loot if you do. the factions are very different and have different goals (Division 2; they feel the same) and each one has they own set of challenges. Each set of equipment matters and it's not just based on gear level (unlike our other friend).
So in conclusion;
if you want to go against all odds and have an amazing open-world experience, then Division 1 is your you.
